      },
      "date": "2013-02-11 16:51:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, approved\n\nThe patch itself seems fine, but fld_rrb_hash() seems somewhat broken?  Does this mean that the FLDB itself is split across all of the MDTs, or is it replicated?  If the FLDB is split, this would break as soon as the number of MDTs is changed? Also, if some MDT is added and then remover, it seems fld_rrb_hash() would LBUG() if the MDT is unavailable?  Better to just fall back and try some other MDT?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "aaaccbae74224445912edf7ba92cd7a24c9ff494",
