      "date": "2013-02-12 08:00:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/52095b00-74e6-11e2-bf59-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
