      "date": "2013-02-15 14:18:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: (2 inline comments)\n\nIf we send all special seq lookup reqs to the MDT0, then is it necessary to send those special seq lookup reqs? Why not skip such seq lookup? Since we already know that the special seqs are all owned by the MDT0?",
