      "date": "2013-02-17 14:56:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/86e698cc-790c-11e2-9a74-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  3 tests failed: replay-ost-single, conf-sanity, sanity.",
